    "desc": "The American Academy of Neurology is dedicated to promoting the highest quality patient-centered care and enhancing member career satisfaction.",
    "navbar": "AAN PUBLICATIONS\nJOIN OR RENEW YOUR MEMBERSHIP\nLOG IN",
    "text": "AAN PUBLICATIONS\nJOIN OR RENEW YOUR MEMBERSHIP\nLOG IN\nEDUCATION\nRESEARCH\nPRACTICE\nMEMBERSHIP\nADVOCACY\nEVENTS\nRESOURCES FOR\nBy continuing to use our site, you agree to the Terms of Use and acknowledge that you’ve read our Privacy Policy. Also, this site uses cookies. Some are essential to make our site work properly, others perform functions more fully described in our Privacy Policy. By continuing to use our site, you consent to the use of these cookies.\nAAN MEMBERSHIP\nExperience all the AAN has to offer + save 30% on the 2023 Annual Meeting!\nLEARN MORE\nRESOURCES FOR THE HIGHEST QUALITY PATIENT-CENTERED NEUROLOGIC CARE\nLog in to access journals and online learning programs.\nNot a Member? JOIN NOW.\nYour source for the latest patient and caregiver information.\nVISIT OUR PATIENT SITE\nAdvertisement\nNEW SYNAPSE APP!\nStaying connected to your AAN sections and member communities just got easier with the new Synapse Member Community app.\nLEARN MORE AND DOWNLOAD\nARE YOU MISSING OUT?\nJoin your 13,000+ colleagues who depend on Continuum & Continuum Audio to stay informed with a $399 yearly member rate\nSUBSCRIBE TODAY\nAAN GUIDELINES\nBrowse clinical practice guidelines to help make decisions on the diagnosis and treatment of neurologic diseases.\nACCESS NOW\nLATEST NEWS\nPRESIDENT'S COLUMN\nJoin Us in Boston—or Live Online—for Our Exciting 75th Annual Meeting\nAT THE MEETINGS\nHighlights from the 2022 American Epilepsy Society Annual Meeting\nNEW STUDY\nCan Diet Combined with Drugs Reduce Seizures?\nAdvertisement\nGUIDELINES & MEASURES\nVIEW ALL\nAPR 2022\nQUALITY MEASURES\nSeizure Frequency Quality Measurement Set\nMAR 2022\nPRACTICE ADVISORY\nStroke Prevention in Symptomatic Large Artery Intracranial Atherosclerosis Practice Advisory\nON DEMAND \n2023 PHYSICIAN FEE SCHEDULE WEBINAR\nLearn about the 2023 Medicare Physician Fee Schedule updates and impacts to neurology\nACCESS NOW\nONLINE \nAPP NEUROLOGY EDUCATION SERIES\nA self-paced, online education series designed especially for neurology APPs.\nLEARN MORE\nAPRIL 22-27 \nAAN ANNUAL MEETING\nJoin us in Boston or live online.\nREGISTER NOW\nMEMBER DIRECTORY\nA member-only tool to search for AAN members.\nACCESS NOW\nCONTACT US\nMEMBERSHIP AND SUPPORT\nABOUT THE AAN\nINCLUSION, DIVERSITY, EQUITY, ANTI-RACISM, AND SOCIAL JUSTICE\nWORK AT THE AAN\nPRESS ROOM\nINDUSTRY\nADVERTISE\nSYNAPSE MEMBER COMMUNITY\nAMERICAN BRAIN FOUNDATION\nTerms of Use Code of Conduct Accessibility Privacy Policy\n©2023 American Academy of Neurology - All Rights Reserved\n👋 Hi Can we help you?",
